Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:54.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}她说着低下了头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:02:01.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这一夜 我流泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:08.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冰冷彻骨 仿如冻雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:15.86,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}洒落的现实 无处可避
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:22.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生存就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.71,0:02:26.33,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仅为这理由而束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:29.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Heart  My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:36.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪光对面 看到了光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:43.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}小小的窗上 映出旧时晴空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:50.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽无法如鸟儿一般飞翔
