Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样伊欧利亚计划的一切都是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫做傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.61,0:00:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.81,0:00:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意识与Veda直连
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉体不过是容器而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做不到的我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过了 我是你们的上位种族
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利冯兹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将 A-LAWS那边好像有点麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该到我出场了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的战果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校 A-LAWS旗舰被击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 截断敌方舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS队 集中攻击舰队中央
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢 慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正规军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 敌舰…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吝惜弹药 跟上联邦军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者不在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方舰队被截断
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这战术…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊安 集中攻击正面中央的舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 琳达
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样突破舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam专心防守母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 Gundam专心防守母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军发来的通信?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是玛内金?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违了 九条
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蒂·玛内金 你怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:57.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是为了制裁A-LAWS而利用你们而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗结束后 再重新追究你们的罪责
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告所有部队 立即进行回避运动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 攻击来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不祥的光线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后方有强力能源反应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗…停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 刚才那巨大的光束是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二发 扫射准备开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 GN Drive交换作业开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光学迷彩 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各员 报告损害情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 右舷损伤 轻微
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON 运输舰 一艘击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS也有20架以上严重损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS舰队 似乎开始撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示在屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地型外宇宙航行母舰「天人」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊欧利亚在两个多世纪以前就预见到了 与未知种族的遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中注定的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive Veda 变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘母舰才是人类的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于灭亡之中拯救人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是方舟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告各舰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们天人即将进攻敌方大型母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始对其中的量子型演算系统Veda的夺还作战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此对一直以来给予协助的众多人士表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时对光荣牺牲的人们表达哀悼之意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞 托勒密的航线转向敌方母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 航线向敌方母舰修正
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺还Veda
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最坏情况即使破坏 也要阻止敌方母舰的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了注定的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是对我们改变世界的赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做个了断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从变革者的支配下解放世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次改变世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了未来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field 最大展开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终任务 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰前进同时寻找入侵航线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各机攻击炮台确保航线畅通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 打开突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被大型炮塔锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没完没了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没轮到我们出场?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gaga部队足以应付
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Gaga：变革者量产型MS，和Gadessa、Garazzo一样\N都是Ga开头，驾驶员为克隆人）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是隐藏角色 希林
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航线上的敌方粒子炮已摧毁57%
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有MS部队出现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有新型机吗 而且密密麻麻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种形状 难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死于自己的技术之下吧 天人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM?
